(1551, 44, '<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width:500px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style="text-align:right">March 27th, 2017<br />\r\n			Dear Parents,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p style="text-align:right">SMKN 1 Padaherang joins the National Education Association (NEA) with a thousand schools nationwide in celebrating the 24th annual Indonesian Education Week from April 19th-24th, 2017. As part of the celebration, we will be organizing &ldquo;Parents Day&rdquo; on Tuesday, April 20th, 2017, to provide you with firsthand look at what the school day is like for your teenager. This initiative is designed to highlight the importance of parental involvement in a teenager&rsquo;s education.<br />\r\n			Our Parents Day will include a wide variety of activities for parents to participate in, including a seminar, school tour, and students&rsquo; art exhibition. The activities taking place throughout the day will also reinforce Indonesian Education Week&rsquo;s tag-line, &ldquo;Great Schools: A Basic Right and Our Responsibility&rdquo;. The tag-line represents NEA&rsquo;s vision of calling upon all Indonesian peopleto do their part in making schools great for every teenager so that they can grow and achieve an the 21st century.<br />\r\n			We request the honor of your participation on this important day. Please fill out the attached form to confirm yours and return it to Ms. Mila of SMKN 1 Padaherang, by April 10, 2017. For more information on Indonesian Education Week, please visit our website st www.indo_edu_week.com.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p style="text-align:right">Sincerely,<br />\r\n			<strong>Nunung Erni</strong><br />\r\n			Dra. Nunung Erni, M.MPd<br />\r\n			Principal</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>What is the purpose of the invitation?</p>\r\n', 1, '', '<p>to invite the student&#39;s parents participating on The Parents Day</p>\r\n', '<p>to inform the students about the parents day</p>\r\n', '<p>to celebrate the student&#39;s graduation</p>\r\n', '<p>to get the parents admitted</p>\r\n', '', 'opt1_soal', '', 1, 1),
