(1569, 44, '<p>43. Read the following invitation letter carefully and answer the question.<br />\r\nDecember 15th, 2019<br />\r\n20 Lake Tondano Street<br />\r\nManado<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width:500px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Dear Denny,</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>I am holding a dinner to celebrate my agency&rsquo;s fifth anniversary, which coincides with my 30th birthday. I would very much like to invite a few of my colleagues to join me on that occasion.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>May I request the pleasure of your company at Hotel Orchid at 7 p.m. on Monday 18th of December?<br />\r\n			Your sincerely yours<br />\r\n			Ipung</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nQuestions :<br />\r\na.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Who is the sender of the invitation?<br />\r\nb.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Why did Ipung write an invitation letter to Denny?<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 2, '', '', '', '', '', '', 'opt1_soal', '<p>Essay</p>\r\n', 1, 1),
(1570, 44, '<p>Read the following text and answer the questions provided below.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width:500px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Rome, Italy<br />\r\n			10 August 2014<br />\r\n			Dear Akmal,&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>It&rsquo;s been a year since we started writing letters to each other. And it&rsquo;s also been a great and enjoyable time for me. It started just as a random thing to do for me, I mean.. I just wanted to have a friend from abroad whom I can write letter to, practice English with, share my experiences, and so on. But after a while, I found a fun doing it and then started to feel happy about it onward.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>So, I want to tell you about my week here&hellip; As I told you, I had to prepare for my college entrance examination. Fortunately, the cram school has already finished this week and I finally get my holiday! Fyuuh, it was tiring and exhausting yet challenging in its own way. Now I feel confident to face my exam at the end of this month.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Then my holiday begins&hellip; And so I was thinking that I have to go on vacation to release the tension and relax for a while before the exam. Then, I was thinking to visit your country, INDONESIA! I&rsquo;ve never been there, but I&rsquo;ve read and heard from my pals that it is such a beautiful country with its vast culture; the views, the mountains, the beaches, aaah..I really want to visit there!<br />\r\n			I have made my mind about it, and I&rsquo;ve already prepared everything. But of course, I want to ask you whether you&rsquo;d have free time or not so we can arrange a meeting, and if possible, accompanying me to explore some places of your lovely country.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>I am planning to start my vacation next week, and if I&rsquo;m not mistaken, it will be your country&rsquo;s independence day by then, right? I hope I won&rsquo;t miss the celebration since I&rsquo;m sure it will be delightful, too. I&rsquo;m really looking forward to hearing from you soon. Let&rsquo;s start packing!!!<br />\r\n			Your pal,<br />\r\n			Ilary Marsha<br />\r\n			P.S. This comes with a souvenir in it.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nQuestions:<br />\r\na.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;What kind of the personal letter is it?<br />\r\nb.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;How did the writer begin his letter?<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 2, '', '', '', '', '', '', 'opt1_soal', '<p>Essay</p>\r\n', 1, 1),
(1571, 44, '<p>Read the following text and answer the questions provided below.<br />\r\nEsia&reg; Reload Voucher<br />\r\n1)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Scratch the grey area with a coin to find 16 digits voucher number.<br />\r\n2)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Dial *900 and follow the instructions or SMS to 555, type TOPUP 16 digits voucher number.<br />\r\n3)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;The amount stated on the voucher will be added to yourasia/Wifone/Wimode account.<br />\r\n4)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Dial *955/*555 or SMS to 555 and type: Talk time to check your remaining talk Time balance &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;from your phone.<br />\r\n5)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Active period 30 days. This could be changed without prior notice. Please Top up before end of &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;active. Customer Care Dial *999 from Esia number or www.myesia.com. Produced by PT Bakrie &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Telecom TBK. Jakarta<br />\r\nQuestions :<br />\r\na.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;What is the purpose of the text above?<br />\r\nb.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&ldquo;This could be changed without prior notice.&rdquo; The word &ldquo;this&rdquo; in the sentences refers to &hellip;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 2, '', '', '', '', '', '', 'opt1_soal', '<p>Essay</p>\r\n', 1, 1);
